segue_the_chain: From a sleeper…to a night train…

segue_dave.line: Sleeper broke up in 1998, while The Herd's "Toorali" was released by Elefant Traks, a record label which was founded in the same year...
segue_dave.explanation: Sleeper was formed as a band in 1998 and The Herd's "Summerland" was released by Elefant Traks, a record label which was founded in the same year.
